        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Student Exchanges with North Korean Schools Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits an institution of higher education (IHE) from receiving certain federal education funds if the IHE has an agreement in effect with an IHE or other organization that is directly funded by the North Korean government.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
